       " Document(metadata={'source': 'files/medical-law-2026-04.pdf', 'coordinates': {'points': ((50.0, 191.0), (50.0, 201.0), (243.30188000000004, 201.0), (243.30188000000004, 191.0)), 'system': 'PixelSpace', 'layout_width': 595.0, 'layout_height': 842.0}, 'file_directory': 'files', 'filename': 'medical-law-2026-04.pdf', 'last_modified': '2026-06-17T21:37:27', 'page_number': 5, 'languages': ['kor'], 'filetype': 'application/pdf', 'parent_id': '689e5c97fbdec106cca7dbd7f67152a6', 'category': 'Title', 'element_id': '55fd896b2c1cd4dd284135e575db9169'}, page_content='는 등 안전관리를 위하여 노력하여야 한다.'),\n",
