       " Document(metadata={'source': 'files/medical-law-2026-04.pdf', 'coordinates': {'points': ((50.0, 223.0), (50.0, 233.0), (310.5600000000001, 233.0), (310.5600000000001, 223.0)), 'system': 'PixelSpace', 'layout_width': 595.0, 'layout_height': 842.0}, 'file_directory': 'files', 'filename': 'medical-law-2026-04.pdf', 'last_modified': '2026-06-17T21:37:27', 'page_number': 23, 'languages': ['kor'], 'filetype': 'application/pdf', 'parent_id': '4b261a682ca2320871fec16383f47a99', 'category': 'Title', 'element_id': 'e8201b39777f730f2649060b933f8a9b'}, page_content='한에 관한 내용을 전자의무기록시스템에 반영하여야 한다.'),\n",
